body_html:
EastCoastDodgeball is putting an end to this unresolved struggle right now. At DODGEBALL 151, season finale headliners and 2008 rivals Grant Cornero and Ryan Letsche clash one last time in their eagerly-awaited rubber match.

2007's Rookie of the Year award winner owned January's DODGEBALL CXX, only for the "Rimshot King" to return to the favor, CREAMation style, just five short weeks later.

This will be Cornero's farewell encounter as the 19 year-old embarks on the journey known as college. Will he be able to overcome his greatest adversary or will Letsche send him down a trail of tears? Attend the 151st presentation, August 16, beginning at 7:15pm.
